				else 
					.nav.fill
						a(href='/') 
							img(src='/images/logo-nav.png')
						a.button.color1.no-border.hiring(href='/jobs') We're Hiring!
						a.button.special(href='mailto:team@siliconunited.com') CONTACT SALES
			
